<head type="main-authorial">AMERICA.</head>
        <div>
<lg type="linegroup">
    <l n="1">Centre of equal daughters, equal sons,</l>
    <l n="2">All, all alike endear'd, grown, ungrown, young or old,</l>
    <l n="3">Strong, ample, fair, enduring, capable, rich,</l>
    <l n="4">Perennial with the Earth, with Freedom, Law and Love,</l>
    <l n="5">A grand, sane, towering, seated Mother,</l>
    <l n="6">Chair'd in the adamant of Time.</l>
</lg></div>
